=Create virtual environment=

The commands below will create a new env with the name we choose, then after activating it we can install the requirements using the command 

{{{bash
" Installing the env 
pip install virtualenv
" Making the env and but its name
virtualenv [name_of_your_project]
" Activaiting the env
name_of_your_project/bin/activate
" Installing the requirements
pip3 install -r requirements
" Deactivating the env
deactivate
}}}

